{"id": 2425, "genre": 1001, "title": "当你对追求者说“不”的时候，对方都有过哪些理解错误？", "description": "你说的“不”，都遇到过哪些误读？（题图来自：iStock © CSA-Printstock ）", "record_count": 2232, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180616160020q86cpsf7YAultSDL.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-06-16T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 287749, "content": "不，这个不算不算，我喜欢你但不是那种喜欢。这该怎么理解？我理解错了，以为是我不够优秀。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1283059}, {"id": 287750, "content": "为什么可以喜欢别人就不可以喜欢我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377197}, {"id": 288008, "content": "说我是同性恋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 882093}, {"id": 287753, "content": "说“不！”之后对方还会死缠烂打...太讨厌了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377213}, {"id": 287754, "content": "对方可能以为：\n“是我做得还不够好，再接再厉”", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1270491}, {"id": 301322, "content": "我不敢说不", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599008}, {"id": 287755, "content": "怕做不成朋友吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377219}, {"id": 287756, "content": "怕做不成朋友。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377219}, {"id": 287757, "content": "以为我“欲迎还拒”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1375831}, {"id": 287760, "content": "认为只要努力对ta好，就一定有收获。但你的好，或许ta并不需要，ta也没必要对你的行动做出任何回应。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1356599}, {"id": 289040, "content": "buyao因为身高拒绝我.", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1382963}, {"id": 287762, "content": "对两个人说过不，当时没有什么感觉，也没可以注意对方心里会怎么想。直到后来被人说了“不”才明白，那一刻感觉失去了半个世界。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372920}, {"id": 289042, "content": "不知道怎么说说不只好晾着……尴尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1383050}, {"id": 287763, "content": "天啊，我有追求者??", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377313}, {"id": 287767, "content": "既然不喜欢我，为什么要每天跟我聊天，为什么要关心我？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377370}, {"id": 288023, "content": "我哪里不好了/我到底有什么不好/那他呢 我哪里比不上他", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377946}, {"id": 290584, "content": "认为我认为ta配不上我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1388767}, {"id": 287769, "content": "以为你的拒绝只是欲拒还迎", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377389}, {"id": 288282, "content": "搞暧昧不在一起是怎么回事？骚的痛？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378622}, {"id": 287771, "content": "会先问为什么不？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1366232}, {"id": 287772, "content": "拒绝了对方我自己很难过，想起了自己曾经被拒绝的心情。48小时了，心情依旧没有平复。 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1253145}, {"id": 287774, "content": "说不得人难道从来没后悔过？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1275599}, {"id": 287775, "content": "没机会说不！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374956}, {"id": 287776, "content": "母胎solo进来看一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088651}, {"id": 287777, "content": "\n\n还没有被拒过", "image": "img/option/option/20180619083617JAsnE6m1YX5NKxi8", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377486}, {"id": 288292, "content": "最可怕的是  这丝毫没有打消他们的积极性\n他们的心态都异常的好", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1319017}, {"id": 289828, "content": "“我有车有房，你还有什么不满意？”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680675}, {"id": 287784, "content": "都没有人追求我???", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1262031}, {"id": 287785, "content": "婉拒被认为还有机会", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372396}, {"id": 287786, "content": "我哪儿来的追求者！？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 364403}, {"id": 288307, "content": "不知道，一般我说不那就是嫉妒讨厌\n懒得想她怎么想的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1378740}, {"id": 293683, "content": "那做朋友呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408249}, {"id": 288052, "content": "这不拒绝一般都是要进行多次才能让对方明白“不”真的就是“不”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377983}, {"id": 288315, "content": "对不起，我改", "image": "img/option/option/20180620161945NC3DytLnOpxfHolc", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377017}, {"id": 287549, "content": "我从来都是被说“不”的.", "image": null, "praise_count": 452, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485810}, {"id": 287550, "content": "我哪里不够好，我自己都把自己感动了，你还好意思说不？", "image": null, "praise_count": 222, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875173}, {"id": 287551, "content": "我没有追求者", "image": null, "praise_count": 182, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1109815}, {"id": 287552, "content": "被拒绝了三年，连在一起以后也经常被拒绝\n我真是个失败者", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1375624}, {"id": 287554, "content": "我是捕食者", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1228484}, {"id": 287555, "content": "“你一定是因为某些外部原因而拒绝我 不是因为不喜欢我”", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 454906}, {"id": 287556, "content": "连说不的机会都没有给过我", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374543}, {"id": 287558, "content": "\"所有命運贈送的禮物,早已在暗中標好了價格\" 我顯然還負擔不起她的代價", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 767579}, {"id": 287559, "content": "没有追求者 单身光棍", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1375976}, {"id": 287560, "content": "作为被说“不”的一方，有时会怀疑是不是她的朋友在搞鬼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1336181}, {"id": 287561, "content": "我不相信，怎么可能   （摊手）", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1242217}, {"id": 287562, "content": "我都被拒绝怕了，回家相亲吧?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374316}, {"id": 287818, "content": "没有过什么误解啊，直接无视我的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377674}, {"id": 287563, "content": "只是时机不对，再坚持一下？", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1375994}, {"id": 287565, "content": "对方：那你喜欢谁？", "image": null, "praise_count": 150, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112484}, {"id": 287566, "content": "我努力就可以", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 575362}]}